{"tid":1322103,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［幫推］大埔連儂隧道解決方法 連儂牆翻新4.0需維穩","createTime":"2019-07-16T00:33:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T05:19:30.000Z","uid":118448,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"0855224b5861bcf8ca1192aac59cc0fa43f6927d","tid":1322103,"uid":118448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T00:33:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">石籬琴日做大翻新 </span></span> <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">下有大埔建議做法</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不能撕毀 可以移位<br />\n為求整齊乾淨  <br />\n容易發放正確資訊</span></span><br />\n<br />\n若果貼其他意見嘅人 反對或者投訴<br />\n可以以需要整理整齊管理連儂牆作理由<br />\n運作連儂牆有其既定方法並非撕毀<br />\n而是保護連儂牆運作<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.連儂牆貼滿問題</span></span>(資訊大量湧入)<br />\n因為有好多區都有貼滿的問題<br />\n(本來大量貼大量memo貼完再蓋memo)<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">(見附件圖1,2,3,4)</span></span><br />\n<br />\n有其他外來者其他言論<br />\n連儂牆充斥不同資訊 <br />\n運作連儂牆的義工身份是整理好確保運作<br />\n<br />\n整理最佳資訊放在頭位 最新現况<br />\n今天716早上人流流量多 所以會企喺度睇<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">(見附件圖5)</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2.解決方法</span></span><br />\n有一啲資訊可能已經過期<br />\n事實上可能有一啲地區會日曬雨淋 <br />\n可能會化開或者根本上看不到發表的言論<br />\n適當嘅時候放棄一啲文宣圖 <br />\n貼上新嘅文宣圖作為替補<br />\n撕左嘅可以將佢重新整理 並非棄掉意見<br />\n資訊要update 最新應該714沙田遊行資訊<br />\n若果唔可以進行大翻身<br />\n*唯有整齊覆蓋佢* <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">大埔例子</span></span><br />\n<br />\n旗應不撕毀<br />\n需大量人手整理<br />\n例如牆有高中低位置<br />\n將置兩邊牆下身（低）位置放旗或者圖<br />\n（中）位置放memo <br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">*若屬於重要位置應放主要資訊*</span><br />\n（高）位置放大字圖或大型可易見文宣圖<br />\n務求做到整理乾淨而美觀<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">最緊要無礙<br />\n最主嘅頭位擺<br />\n最update資訊！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n可以將主題歸主題<br />\n整理之後再移位 <br />\n並非撕毀其他人意見<br />\n因為基於無論佢係公眾地方定私人地方<br />\n只有執法人員可以進行撕毀行動<br />\n連儂牆發起人則屬於他的擁有 <br />\n它可以管理並且確保其運作<br />\n只有執法人員能夠剝奪<br />\n<br />\n每一區情況不同但是同樣地有一個目標<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">整齊乾淨<br />\n發放最新最正確資訊</span></span><br />\n附件1<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2PYq8cM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2PYq8cM.png&h=593d4e91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n附件2<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WiDuQq7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWiDuQq7.png&h=61951f97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n附件3<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RLCjtcP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRLCjtcP.png&h=f39d5b5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n附件4<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/02Je1xQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F02Je1xQ.png&h=4ac1be6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n附件5<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z58bjjw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz58bjjw.png&h=b9ade32d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"230bdab102e853527cee56de6200d1850d78a249","tid":1322103,"uid":118448,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T00:33:35.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2804dfb105e898a8036c003a1305b7bc45fa71b","tid":1322103,"uid":118448,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T00:34:17.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3120949eb60d3637744d53572e39246bfaf3d4ff","tid":1322103,"uid":12609,"like":2,"dislike":12,"score":-10,"citedBy":2,"repl